                "text": "Twice per day, when a masked assassin dons a mask or other full-face covering, they can instantaneously take on the appearance of any creature they\u2019ve seen in person within the past 24 hours. A creature must succeed at a Perception check to realize this is a disguise (DC = 20 + 1.5 \u00d7 the masked assassin\u2019s CR). This effect lasts for 10 minutes or until the effect is ended.",
